Package: work.tkgstrator.warsenginebridge
Name: WarsEngineBridge
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: ShogiWars CSA engine bridge tweak. Embeds a CSA TCP server (port 4081) inside the ShogiWars process so any CSA-protocol engine on the same LAN can play against or observe the live board. Companion to KiouEngineBridge. For authorized testing only.
Maintainer: NEVER KNOWS BEST
Author: tkgstrator
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
